.SH NAME
openssl\-rand \- generate pseudo\-random bytes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
\&\fBopenssl rand\fR
[\fB\-help\fR]
[\fB\-out\fR \fIfile\fR]
[\fB\-base64\fR]
[\fB\-hex\fR]
